{"tid":2338357,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"串謀暴動案 官促避免「後見之明」","createTime":"2020-12-24T03:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a23f49ac5eadb64534388225d656989f0d0455ec","tid":2338357,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/DEGA647DKVGIROPBX2S7JRWP2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FDEGA647DKVGIROPBX2S7JRWP2Q%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MerkGmmZttFFipzpmUasbQ8%3D&h=3eb18b86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FDEGA647DKVGIROPBX2S7JRWP2Q%2F&h=eb465ade\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/DEGA647DKVGIROPBX2S7JRWP2Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n串謀暴動案 官促避免「後見之明」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p_meGaO_BtgUFZFFLnHbEByoIvQ=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JU5NAIRTA5E6JLGTSLWZVGGGKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp_meGaO_BtgUFZFFLnHbEByoIvQ%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJU5NAIRTA5E6JLGTSLWZVGGGKE.jpg&h=2a5c0e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沈小民<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方去年10月1日在銅鑼灣。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n控方指控第三。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控辯兩周內補充書面陳詞<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，第四被告在單位出現或只是聯誼，就算「佢哋係有啲古怪㗎啦，都唔一定係串謀暴動」；亦沒有證據顯示第五被告對涉案物品知情。而控方不再指第六被告租用單位，難以推論至他串謀暴動。沈官其後提出如何在本案中避免出現「Hindsight bias（後見之明偏誤）」的問題，「大家都知道10月1號發生咩事，亦知往後嘅日子發生咗咩事，係咪好容易諗當時咁嘅社會環境，推斷佢哋一定係參加暴動呢？」又謂：「但如果你將事件放喺今日度睇，咁又可能唔同晒啦喎」，並問「係咪忘記晒當日往後發生過嘅嘢，去判斷佢哋係參加暴動定非法集結呢？」控辯雙方兩星期內向法庭補充書面陳詞。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC908、918/20"},{"pid":"22014ece4b6e9e4f29bff635fd7305ae963abf3e","tid":2338357,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb66b99aff6c53da886ae9d0d95327ef20727001","tid":2338357,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"Hindsight bias<br />\n<br />\n呢個真係好易中伏"}]}